            <p>Additional materials about the Greater Hartford Process are available in the 
                <extref ns2:href="http://www.lib.uconn.edu/online/research/speclib/ASC/findaids/lumsden/MSS20060243.html">Arthur Lumsden Papers</extref> and interviews with associated individuals in the 
                <extref ns2:href="http://www.lib.uconn.edu/online/research/speclib/ASC/findaids/COH/MSS19840025.html#series16">Center for Oral History Interviews Collection</extref>.</p>
            <p>
